data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream home in Pasadena Golf Club Estates! This beautifully remodeled 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers an unparalleled blend of modern elegance and classic comfort, perfect for those seeking a luxurious yet cozy living experience.  Master Bedroom Retreat: Step into the spacious master bedroom, a sanctuary of relaxation, boasting a generous walk-in closet and a private en-suite bath. Luxuriate in the thoughtfully designed master bath, complete with contemporary fixtures, a granite topped vanity, and a tub with shower.  Modern Kitchen: The heart of this home is its stunning kitchen, featuring top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and custom cabinetry with backsplash. The walk-in pantry provides ample storage, making this kitchen a haven for culinary enthusiasts.  Oversized Garage: The convenience of an oversized garage cannot be overstated. With plenty of space for two cars and additional storage, you'll have room for all your vehicles and recreational gear.  Covered Rear Patio: Enjoy the Florida sunshine year-round on your covered rear patio. Whether you're sipping morning coffee or hosting evening gatherings, this outdoor space is perfect for both relaxation and entertainment.  Completely Remodeled: This home has been meticulously remodeled to offer you the best in modern living. From the freshly painted exterior to the stylish interior finishes, no detail has been overlooked. Move-in ready and designed for comfort.  Pasadena Golf Club Estates is a sought-after community known for its tranquil atmosphere and proximity to everything you need. You'll appreciate the nearby parks, golf courses, shopping centers, and excellent schools.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning Pasadena Golf Club Estates home your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the epitome of luxury living in beautiful Florida. Act quickly, as homes of this caliber tend to sell fast!
